1000008800670@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Thus the ⌊>India>⌋n epic, the ⌊/⌊>Ramayana>⌋/⌋, appears in many versions in the various ⌊>Indian languages>⌋, and the stories are different in each.@@@@1@22@@oe@26-8-2013
