1000009000880@unknown@formal@none@1@S@If, as Turing puts it, "the interrogator decide[s] wrongly as often when the game is played [with the computer] as he does when the game is played between a man and a woman", then it can be argued that the computer is intelligent.@@@@1@43@@oe@26-8-2013
